# Task 2.1 — Unify wrapper pages by template (manual now, auto later)

All SEO wrapper pages should share one minimal HTML template. For this stage, they can be copied manually, changing only:

• slug
• title
• description
• OpenGraph metadata

This keeps the HTML consistent and prepares the project for registry-driven generation in the next stage.

