# Result of This Refactoring Stage

After completing these tasks the site will:

• expose crawlable URLs for each artwork
• use path-based routing as the primary routing model
• keep the existing shell + registry + runtime architecture
• provide SEO entry pages for artworks
• include metadata for search engines
• support social preview cards
• expose a sitemap for search engines

This establishes the **SEO foundation layer** on top of the existing generative-art runtime.

